Code and tables

Syntax highlighting

Here is a sample code chunk, just to show that syntax highlighting works as expected.

library(palmerpenguins)
library(glue)

say_hello <- function (name) {
  glue("Hello, {name} !")
}

say_hello("world")
Hello, world !
